values:
I think i can wave goodbye to my distinctions. It wasn't as easy as i've expected it to be but at the same time it wasn't really that difficult. Okay i know i'm contradicting myself but my point is, no more distinction lah. I should be happy if i could get a B grade already.&nbsp;

Finally, tomorrow i'm able to go for choir prac! Its been like 10000 years or something since i've been for prac because it clashes with school. And i'll get to see my all time favourite people, which i've been neglecting since May till now.

SIGH....

Work seemed like forever today. I did struggle to stay awake and it was kinda busy for me. Ben was suppose to come in at 2.30pm but some how or rather he didn't, and we were short of staff today. So when the crowd came in and i was working alone, it was no fun. I was frantically trying to get this and do that, the phone rang non stop for some reason and i was VERY tired.&nbsp;

On a lighter note, i got myself a Dior eyeliner. I love it! But there are still stuff that i needa get, like a whole list of them.

You know, i've been thinking of getting a tattoo for good. Just haven decided on the design yet. Any suggestions?
